						<td>Journey to Dragon Necropolis</td>
						
						<td>Saturday February 9, 2002</td>
						<td>06:00 PM MST</td>
						<td>Ludarian</td>
					</tr>
					
					<tr>
						<td colspan="4">
						We have an opportunity to raid Dragon Necropolis this Saturday.  I am to select 2 people from our guild (49+) to go for sure and represetnt us, all others will have to show up and hope for a spot.  This is going to be a very advanced raid, with a lot of travel, so a minimum time commitment of 4 hours is necessary.  The longer we stay the more we get to do.  If you want to be one of the two that gets a for sure spot, post a message to <a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fepicshadowsfrm18.showMessage?topicID=55.topic" target="_new">this post</a> in our forum or e-mail me.</td>
