			    <td colspan="2" bgcolor="#505050"> 
			      
			      <block>The Shadows pulled together a late night rush last night to work on a couple of quest drops that we needed to obtain. Akronis and Sabrar obtained the orbs needed from Sol B for the SK quest spell, life leech, then Gorabok, Ludarian, Elles and the two Shadow Knights proceeded to Trak's Teeth for some Sebilis key farming. After hooking Ludarian and Sabrar up with their Trak idols to get into Sebilis, our next stop was Permafrost, where after a couple long, hard hours where the puller was struggling with LD and chronic FD failures, we managed to net two prickly pears, also for the SK quest spell. Many thanks to all the Shadows that gave their support, Manluin and Kevy included, who were not mentioned in the list above.</block> </td>
