			    <td colspan="2" bgcolor="#505050"> 
			      
			      <block>After a weekend full of so much activity it's fun to look back and see all that happened. ES had 2 runner ups in the Kamikazee halfling run, and Lobo won the sub 45 royal rumble!  Also, ES did really well in the scavenger hunt.  We could say that we might have been tied in second :), but the big prize went to Razor's Edge.  A special thanks goes to everyone who made all of the events possible.  That includes those who helped donate money for the 2k and prize fund, and also those who helped gather that money and helped out in the scavenger hunt group.  Everyone's strong spirit and willingness to help the guild out really helped to show everyone what we're made of.  It's great to play this game with you all!</block> </td>
